A **PPF (Public Provident Fund) calculator** estimates the maturity value of annual investments in a PPF account at the current government-declared interest rate. The current PPF interest rate is **7.1% per annum** (effective since October 2023), compounded annually.

PPF offers EEE (Exempt-Exempt-Exempt) tax status: contributions qualify for Section 80C deduction (up to ₹1.5 lakh), interest earned is fully tax-free, and the maturity amount is completely exempt from income tax — making it one of the most tax-efficient savings instruments available in India.
